{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-template-js","path":"/java/start-gradle-project/gradle-project-init/","result":{"data":{"cur":{"id":"3bc1d196-d3f7-535a-a058-120877231f96","html":"<h2 id=\"개요\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EA%B0%9C%EC%9A%94\" aria-label=\"개요 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>개요</h2>\n<hr>\n<p>Mac 환경에서 Gradle Proejct 를 생성하는 방법에 대해서 알아보겠습니다.</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"center\">종류</th>\n<th>환경</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">OS</td>\n<td>M1 Mac(Monterey 12.4)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">IDE</td>\n<td>Intellij(2022.1.2)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">Java</td>\n<td>jdk17 (temurin)</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h2 id=\"gralde-프로젝트-시작하기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#gralde-%ED%94%84%EB%A1%9C%EC%A0%9D%ED%8A%B8-%EC%8B%9C%EC%9E%91%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"gralde 프로젝트 시작하기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Gralde 프로젝트 시작하기</h2>\n<hr>\n<h3 id=\"gradle-install-hombrew\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#gradle-install-hombrew\" aria-label=\"gradle install hombrew permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Gradle Install Hombrew</h3>\n<p><a href=\"images/https://gradle.org/install/\">Gradle Installation Documents</a></p>\n<p>Gradle 공식 문서에 따라 설치하도록 합니다. Hombrew 로 설치하는 것 역시 권장 방법이므로 터미널에 다음과 같이 입력 후 실행합니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">brew <span class=\"token function\">install</span> gradle</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"1-프로젝트-시작-폴더-생성\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-%ED%94%84%EB%A1%9C%EC%A0%9D%ED%8A%B8-%EC%8B%9C%EC%9E%91-%ED%8F%B4%EB%8D%94-%EC%83%9D%EC%84%B1\" aria-label=\"1 프로젝트 시작 폴더 생성 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1. 프로젝트 시작 폴더 생성</h3>\n<p>Gradle 프로젝트를 생성하기 전에 해당 프로젝트를 시작할 폴더를 새로 만듭니다. 폴더 명과 별개로 프로젝트 이름은 따로 지정할 수도 있습니다. 방법은 아래 말씀드리겠습니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"> <span class=\"token comment\"># ex) mkdir 프로젝트_폴더_이름</span>\n\n <span class=\"token function\">mkdir</span> demo-java\n\n <span class=\"token comment\"># 생성한 프로젝트로 이동</span>\n <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">cd</span> demo-java</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"2-gradle-프로젝트-생성\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-gradle-%ED%94%84%EB%A1%9C%EC%A0%9D%ED%8A%B8-%EC%83%9D%EC%84%B1\" aria-label=\"2 gradle 프로젝트 생성 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2. Gradle 프로젝트 생성</h3>\n<p>폴더로 이동한 후에 아래 명령어를 입력합니다. 입력 후에는 몇 가지 옵션을 선택하여 프로젝트를 새로 생성합니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">gradle init</code></pre></div>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 660px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 25.555555555555554%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"stat gradle new project\"\n        title=\"stat gradle new project\"\n        src=\"/static/863201865cf52b583e00a95b8a8b04d2/1f083/project-init-1.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/863201865cf52b583e00a95b8a8b04d2/e9ff0/project-init-1.png 180w,\n/static/863201865cf52b583e00a95b8a8b04d2/f21e7/project-init-1.png 360w,\n/static/863201865cf52b583e00a95b8a8b04d2/1f083/project-init-1.png 660w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>생성하고자 하는 프로젝트의 타입을 선택합니다. 저는 이번에 2, “application”을 선택하여 진행하겠습니다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 658px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 22.22222222222222%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAAECAYAAACOXx+WAAAACXBIWXMAAAsTAAALEwEAmpwYAAAAWklEQVQY062POwoAIRQDX+dfRFBREbz/JWdx622ELYakSUIk58wYg1or3nustWitSSm9KiJ3KKVYa1FKuQ9/4Zxj701r7Z/Cc3nOSe8dYwwxRkIIrz9jR2+uPzHhVDcACwltAAAAAElFTkSuQmCC'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"language_select\"\n        title=\"language_select\"\n        src=\"/static/7e0273a4499c67e4cc15c258b02d3842/889a4/project-init-2.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/7e0273a4499c67e4cc15c258b02d3842/e9ff0/project-init-2.png 180w,\n/static/7e0273a4499c67e4cc15c258b02d3842/f21e7/project-init-2.png 360w,\n/static/7e0273a4499c67e4cc15c258b02d3842/889a4/project-init-2.png 658w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 658px) 100vw, 658px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>다음은 프로젝트의 언어를 선택합니다. 저는 “java”를 선택하겠습니다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 656px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 11.11111111111111%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAACCAYAAABYBvyLAAAACXBIWXMAAAsTAAALEwEAmpwYAAAATElEQVQI15XMuw3AIAwAUZuCj0EyEg2Ihv2XPJRMkBTXXPFkjME5h703MUZKKaSUEJHfqSrygGst5pyYGe5OrZXWGr13cs7vDyF8Ai+HAirTcZEUSwAAAABJRU5ErkJggg=='); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"bulid script dsl\"\n        title=\"bulid script dsl\"\n        src=\"/static/36e5e2f36afb9f0407863f230dec2808/748f4/project-init-3.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/36e5e2f36afb9f0407863f230dec2808/e9ff0/project-init-3.png 180w,\n/static/36e5e2f36afb9f0407863f230dec2808/f21e7/project-init-3.png 360w,\n/static/36e5e2f36afb9f0407863f230dec2808/748f4/project-init-3.png 656w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 656px) 100vw, 656px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>다음은 script DSL을 선택합니다. 저는 “groovy”를 선택하겠습니다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 661px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 21.666666666666668%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAAECAYAAACOXx+WAAAACXBIWXMAAAsTAAALEwEAmpwYAAAAbklEQVQY052QOwoAIRQDVUREQbEQxC9+7n/FLD7YemGLaVJMQlgIAbVWtNZgrYVzDlJKMMb+oZTCGIOknPP/opeUEq3rvRM5Z1r54r2HMQZaa9zyT+GckyR7bxKec1BKwc3XWogx4pbeG4QQn8IHee9X087By/YAAAAASUVORK5CYII='); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"select_test_framwork\"\n        title=\"select_test_framwork\"\n        src=\"/static/31ba56aad2af9be476b32902cca80a5d/0012b/project-init-4.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/31ba56aad2af9be476b32902cca80a5d/e9ff0/project-init-4.png 180w,\n/static/31ba56aad2af9be476b32902cca80a5d/f21e7/project-init-4.png 360w,\n/static/31ba56aad2af9be476b32902cca80a5d/0012b/project-init-4.png 661w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 661px) 100vw, 661px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>다음은 테스트 프레임워크를 선택합니다. 선택할 수 있는 테스트 프레임워크는 여러개가 존재하지만 저는 “junit jufiter”를 선택하겠습니다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 577px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 12.777777777777777%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAADCAYAAACTWi8uAAAACXBIWXMAAAsTAAALEwEAmpwYAAAAhUlEQVQI111OwQrFIAzT60BkTufcEFF0HsT//7w8Wthg7xCSpm1a4ZzDdV04zxMhBFBN2nvPNel933mGesdxQCkFIQSklJBSsH5hjOHl3jtSSrjvG7VWRinlZQpfloVDPgH/yDnzQmuNec6JGCN/Yq1l7zk0xmD/+Zbm6JDWGuu6Yts2/ADBX0qj8yyrxgAAAABJRU5ErkJggg=='); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"insert_project_name\"\n        title=\"insert_project_name\"\n        src=\"/static/9eec2dbffa1857ec427ccbf7f542587e/065e2/project-init-5.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/9eec2dbffa1857ec427ccbf7f542587e/e9ff0/project-init-5.png 180w,\n/static/9eec2dbffa1857ec427ccbf7f542587e/f21e7/project-init-5.png 360w,\n/static/9eec2dbffa1857ec427ccbf7f542587e/065e2/project-init-5.png 577w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 577px) 100vw, 577px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>다음은 프로젝트 명을 입력합니다. 디폴트 값은 폴더의 이름을 따라가지만 다른 프로젝트 명을 입력할 수도 있습니다.</p>\n<p>설정을 전부 끝마쳤다면 설정한 옵션에 맞춰 Gradle 프로젝트가 생성됩니다.</p>\n<div class=\"table-of-contents\">\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#%EA%B0%9C%EC%9A%94\">개요</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#gralde-%ED%94%84%EB%A1%9C%EC%A0%9D%ED%8A%B8-%EC%8B%9C%EC%9E%91%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\">Gralde 프로젝트 시작하기</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#gradle-install-hombrew\">Gradle Install Hombrew</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#1-%ED%94%84%EB%A1%9C%EC%A0%9D%ED%8A%B8-%EC%8B%9C%EC%9E%91-%ED%8F%B4%EB%8D%94-%EC%83%9D%EC%84%B1\">1. 프로젝트 시작 폴더 생성</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#2-gradle-%ED%94%84%EB%A1%9C%EC%A0%9D%ED%8A%B8-%EC%83%9D%EC%84%B1\">2. Gradle 프로젝트 생성</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>","excerpt":"개요 Mac 환경에서 Gradle Proejct 를 생성하는 방법에 대해서 알아보겠습니다. 종류 환경 OS M1 Mac(Monterey 12.4) IDE Intellij(2022.1.2) Java jdk17 (temurin) Gralde 프로젝트 시작하기 Gradle Install Hombrew Gradle Installation Documents Gradle 공식 문서에 따라 설치하도록 합니다. Hombrew 로 설치하는 것 역시 권장 방법이므로 터미널에 다음과 같이 입력 후 실행합니다. 1. 프로젝트 시작 폴더 생성 Gradle 프로젝트를 생성하기 전에 해당 프로젝트를 시작할 폴더를 새로 만듭니다. 폴더 명과 별개로 프로젝트 이름은 따로 지정할 수도 있습니다. 방법은 아래 말씀드리겠습니다. 2. Gradle 프로젝트 생성 폴더로 이동한 후에 아래 명령어를 입력합니다. 입력 후에는 몇 가지 옵션을 선택하여 프로젝트를 새로 생성합니다.  생성하고자 하는 프로젝트의 타입을 선택합니다…","frontmatter":{"date":"January 28, 2022","title":"[Gradle] Gradle project 시작하기","categories":"java","author":"chanjin_ahn","emoji":"👻"},"fields":{"slug":"/java/start-gradle-project/gradle-project-init/"}},"next":{"id":"7b5e23a1-2eeb-5e00-864c-63f675574dfe","html":"<h2 id=\"들어가기에-앞서\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%93%A4%EC%96%B4%EA%B0%80%EA%B8%B0%EC%97%90-%EC%95%9E%EC%84%9C\" aria-label=\"들어가기에 앞서 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>들어가기에 앞서</h2>\n<hr>\n<h3 id=\"undertow-란\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#undertow-%EB%9E%80\" aria-label=\"undertow 란 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Undertow 란?</h3>\n<p>Undertow 란 bloking/non-blo 작업 모두에 사용할 수 있도록 설계된 웹 서버입니다.</p>\n<h3 id=\"tomcat-대신-undertow-로-바꿔야-하는-이유\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#tomcat-%EB%8C%80%EC%8B%A0-undertow-%EB%A1%9C-%EB%B0%94%EA%BF%94%EC%95%BC-%ED%95%98%EB%8A%94-%EC%9D%B4%EC%9C%A0\" aria-label=\"tomcat 대신 undertow 로 바꿔야 하는 이유 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Tomcat 대신 Undertow 로 바꿔야 하는 이유</h3>\n<p>아주 오랜시간동안 Tomcat 이 쓰여 익숙하지만, 단지 그 이유 하나만으로 Tocmat 을 써야하는 것은 나쁘다고 생각합니다.</p>\n<p>여러 벤치마크 결과에 따르면 Undertow 는 Tomcat 보다 더 빠르고 가볍고 안정적이고 더 많은 부하를 처리할 수 있습니다.\n관련 커뮤니티도 잘 갖춰져 있기 때문에 제약이 크지 않다면 Tomcat 보다는 Undertow 를 사용하는 것이 더 합리적이라고 생각합니다.</p>\n<h3 id=\"적용-환경\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%A0%81%EC%9A%A9-%ED%99%98%EA%B2%BD\" aria-label=\"적용 환경 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>적용 환경</h3>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>항목</th>\n<th>버전</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>build tool</td>\n<td>gradle 7.3.2</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>application config</td>\n<td>application.yml</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h2 id=\"내장-was-를-undertow-로-변경하기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%82%B4%EC%9E%A5-was-%EB%A5%BC-undertow-%EB%A1%9C-%EB%B3%80%EA%B2%BD%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"내장 was 를 undertow 로 변경하기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>내장 WAS 를 Undertow 로 변경하기</h2>\n<hr>\n<h3 id=\"기존-was-인-tomcat-을-제외\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EA%B8%B0%EC%A1%B4-was-%EC%9D%B8-tomcat-%EC%9D%84-%EC%A0%9C%EC%99%B8\" aria-label=\"기존 was 인 tomcat 을 제외 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>기존 WAS 인 Tomcat 을 제외</h3>\n<p>Tomcat은 사용하지 않을 예정이므로 제외합니다.\n제외하지 않을 경우 에러가 발생할 수 있으니 꼭 제외할 수 있도록 합니다.</p>\n<p>의존성 관리는 build.gradle 에서 할 수 있습니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"yaml\"><pre class=\"language-yaml\"><code class=\"language-yaml\">configurations <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    all<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        // was tomcat 제외\n        <span class=\"token key atrule\">exclude module</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'spring-boot-starter-tomcat'</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"undertow-의존성-추가\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#undertow-%EC%9D%98%EC%A1%B4%EC%84%B1-%EC%B6%94%EA%B0%80\" aria-label=\"undertow 의존성 추가 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Undertow 의존성 추가</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"yaml\"><pre class=\"language-yaml\"><code class=\"language-yaml\">dependencies <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token key atrule\">implementation group</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'org.springframework.boot'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token key atrule\">name</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'spring-boot-starter-undertow'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token key atrule\">version</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'2.6.3'</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"undertow-설정-추가\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#undertow-%EC%84%A4%EC%A0%95-%EC%B6%94%EA%B0%80\" aria-label=\"undertow 설정 추가 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Undertow 설정 추가</h2>\n<p>기본값이 정해져 있지만 필요에 따라 Undertow 설정을 추가합니다. 설정은 application.yml 에서 할 수 있습니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"yaml\"><pre class=\"language-yaml\"><code class=\"language-yaml\">\n<span class=\"token key atrule\">spring</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token key atrule\">server</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n      <span class=\"token key atrule\">port</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">8080</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"결과-확인\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EA%B2%B0%EA%B3%BC-%ED%99%95%EC%9D%B8\" aria-label=\"결과 확인 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>결과 확인</h2>\n<hr>\n<p>정상적으로 바뀌었는지 확인하기 위해서는 서버를 기동하고 로그를 확인해봅니다.</p>\n<h3 id=\"기존-tomcat-환경\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EA%B8%B0%EC%A1%B4-tomcat-%ED%99%98%EA%B2%BD\" aria-label=\"기존 tomcat 환경 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>기존 Tomcat 환경</h3>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 720px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 26.111111111111107%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"tomcat\"\n        title=\"tomcat\"\n        src=\"/static/e7132d9cd8eb425002e2062cd55a675a/37523/3-01-tomcat.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/e7132d9cd8eb425002e2062cd55a675a/e9ff0/3-01-tomcat.png 180w,\n/static/e7132d9cd8eb425002e2062cd55a675a/f21e7/3-01-tomcat.png 360w,\n/static/e7132d9cd8eb425002e2062cd55a675a/37523/3-01-tomcat.png 720w,\n/static/e7132d9cd8eb425002e2062cd55a675a/302a4/3-01-